== Overview ==

Final Fantasy IV features 12 playable characters, each with unique abilities and growth patterns. Unlike other Final Fantasy games, party composition is determined by the story.

== Character Data Structure ==

Each character entry is 64 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Character ID
|-
| $01 || 1 || Current level
|-
| $02-$03 || 2 || Current HP
|-
| $04-$05 || 2 || Max HP
|-
| $06-$07 || 2 || Current MP
|-
| $08-$09 || 2 || Max MP
|-
| $0A || 1 || Strength
|-
| $0B || 1 || Agility
|-
| $0C || 1 || Vitality
|-
| $0D || 1 || Intellect
|-
| $0E || 1 || Spirit
|-
| $0F || 1 || Attack
|-
| $10 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $11 || 1 || Magic Defense
|-
| $12 || 1 || Evasion
|-
| $13 || 1 || Magic Evasion
|-
| $14-$1B || 8 || Equipment slots
|-
| $1C-$3F || 36 || Status, spell slots
|}

